，本身用緊2012mid 既mbp13&rdquo;, 已經用左五年啦<br />\n我自己就唔會用呢部laptop打機，平時會用Adobe ps,premier, ae，間唔中都會用maya, unity同少少VS, 其實係咪用dell好啲<br />\n但係用開蘋果野又鐘意佢個os多啲，不過講硬件既話，新mbp性價比又好似低啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"我用緊mbp 2010，自己換左個ssd, 同加到10gb ram，我自己放工寫program 同上網都無問題<br />\n<br />\n不過都等緊apple intel 8th generation mbp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"巴打部機會唔會好易熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我換左ssd行fushion drive，但好似易熱sor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"我唔會好易熱喎<br />\n我剩用samsung evo 850 256gb，無fusion<br />\n換完果下好似新機咁"},{"pid":"3cddeb0dc696e7a44f932f9be6c37c11676317ff","tid":733782,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"唔好買MacBook Pro<br />\n<br />\n過來人話畀你聽一定唔好買<br />\n<br />\n一嚟Overpriced，個Spec完全唔值個價錢<br />\n<br />\n二嚟好多硬件問題，個Keyboard 已經唔係個個啱用，好彩嘅就覺得好打，之但係幾好多打都好，佢都會好易壞<br />\n<br />\n三，個Keyboard 好食塵，個Mon同Keyboard 做到好少Margin，所以Mon嗰面一受壓就會壓花Mon。除非你每次用都清乾淨個Keyboard，唔係你個mon一定有啲花痕<br />\n<br />\n四，個Mon有問題，好多人個mon都出咗背光問題，detail自己Google，我都中咗招，一整就4200<br />\n<br />\n樓主，我話你知，絕對唔值得成萬幾蚊買部垃圾翻嚟，以前會話Apple Product 係高級工藝品，而家淪為垃圾瑕疵品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aac9f43d0f49f8cef3e530cb4bc5b16db362a92","tid":733782,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ec9ab869da546af73bb6c61f934939a08405124","tid":733782,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"問題係你寫開unity 或者 swift / objc 即係話你一定會用到Xcode <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而Xcode 又一定係綁死macOS , 你諗下成皮幾野買部機，你估我唔想轉window咩，同等價錢買部window 機，真係好勁，問題係轉唔到，有d人話你裝hackatosh 囉。<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊，快咁多時間睇佢個OS 點hack 又要intel U, 又要成日更新，我都剩係想正正常常打下code 姐，搞到咁就局住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7ec14b6aea3dd8b5f8899e7fa9889794e66f92","tid":733782,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"由dell轉左3叔 又ok"}]}